{"type": "article", "id": 12929, "title": "包装袋封口夹", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-03T07:39:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133919iCFE7J8kPrlYTGLX.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自以色列的设计工作室 Peleg Design 推出的一款包装袋封口夹，用来重新密封已经打开的包装袋，尤其适用于最常见的食物包装。设计师把夹子设计成了搭扣钱包的模样，看上去让包装袋变得时尚了不少。目前产品又白、红、绿三种颜色可以选择，一大一小搭配出售，这是<a href=\"http://www.peleg-design.com/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140610qUAm91Qr0Ys8HZNF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81784841\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261406114fVyPSeUEh2BuLqX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140612vH9x4O0djeahrRsF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140613fhjdEyagI8oGbq9D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77383863\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140613oOtPCukrlWGv7wA9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69804401\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\r\n<span></span>\n\n\n\n"}